{{Politics of Singapore}}
'''2015年新加坡大選'''在2015年9月11日舉行<ref name="O1"/>。本次選舉是新加坡建國總理[[李光耀|李光耀]][[李光耀之死|逝世]]後該國舉行的第一次大選，選出了新一屆[[新加坡國會|新加坡國會]]全部89個民選議席。執政的[[人民行動黨|人民行動黨]]（行動黨）雖然在所有選區都面臨反對派挑戰，不過最終仍然贏得89席當中的83席，蟬聯執政。

== 背景 ==
=== 政治制度與政局 ===
《[[新加坡憲法|新加坡共和國憲法]]》<ref>[[新加坡憲法|Constitution of the Republic of Singapore]] ([http://statutes.agc.gov.sg/aol/search/display/view.w3p;page=0;query=DocId%3Acf2412ff-fca5-4a64-a8ef-b95b8987728e%20Depth%3A0%20Status%3Ainforce;rec=0 1985 Rev. Ed., 1999 Reprint] {{Wayback|url=http://statutes.agc.gov.sg/aol/search/display/view.w3p;page=0;query=DocId%3Acf2412ff-fca5-4a64-a8ef-b95b8987728e%20Depth%3A0%20Status%3Ainforce;rec=0 |date=20170220102606 }}).</ref>規定新加坡採納[[代議民主制|代議民主制]]，當中由[[新加坡國籍法|新加坡公民]]經[[新加坡選舉|選舉]]選出的代議士會組建[[新加坡政府|政府]]，並代表他們統治新加坡<ref>{{Singapore Hansard|mp=Lee Hsien Loong|mplink=李顯龍|office=[[新加坡財政部|Minister for Finance]]|title=Government of Singapore Investment Corporation (Disclosure of Annual Accounts)|url=http://sprs.parl.gov.sg/search/topic.jsp?currentTopicID=00068029-ZZ|date=16 May 2001|volume=73|column=1671}}.</ref>。行動黨自[[1959年新加坡大選|1959年大選]]以來，一直都能夠在大選中贏得大多數國會議席，並成為執政黨<ref>{{cite web |author=Kelley Bryan |author2=Gail Davidson |author3=Margaret Stanier |title=Rule of Law in Singapore: Independence of the Judiciary and the Legal Profession in Singapore |url=http://www.singaporedemocrat.org/LRWC.Rule.of.Law.in.Singapore.17.Oct.07.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h3yrsdum?url=http://www.singaporedemocrat.org/LRWC.Rule.of.Law.in.Singapore.17.Oct.07.pdf |archivedate=2009-05-26 |publisher=Lawyers' Rights Watch Canada |work=[[新加坡民主黨|Singapore Democratic Party]] |date=2007-10-17 |quote=In the 1959 elections, the People's Action Party (PAP), led by Lee Kuan Yew, took power and formed the government. The PAP has won all eleven general elections since. In fact, in nearly fifty years, the PAP has never won less than 95 percent of the parliamentary seats, and in recent years a large number of PAP candidates have run unopposed |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-08-22 }}</ref>{{efn|新加坡歷屆大選的詳細結果都可以在新加坡選舉局的網頁查閱<ref>{{cite web|title=Parliamentary Elections Results|url=http://www.eld.gov.sg/elections_past_parliamentary.html|publisher=Singapore Elections Department|access-date=2015-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910073201/http://www.eld.gov.sg/elections_past_parliamentary.html|archive-date=2015-09-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。}}，但在[[2011年新加坡大選|2011年大選]]當中，由於當地民眾對移民、收入不平均和生活費增加的不滿，行動黨得票率創獨立以來新低之餘，還在[[阿裕尼集選區|阿裕尼集選區]]被反對黨[[工人黨_(新加坡)|工人黨]]擊敗，喪失該選區所有議席，這是當地[[集選區|集選區]]制度創設以來行動黨在集選區的競逐中落敗的首例<ref name="blp">{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-05-07/singapore-s-people-s-action-party-keeps-parliamentary-majority-state-says|title=Singapore's Lee Retains Power With Smallest Margin Since 1965|author1=Shamim Adam|last2=Lim|first2=Weiyi|date=2011-05-08|work=Bloomberg Business|publisher=Bloomberg L.P.|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2015-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828214125/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-05-07/singapore-s-people-s-action-party-keeps-parliamentary-majority-state-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，行動黨又於2013年[[2013年新加坡補選|榜鵝東區補選]]中被工人黨擊敗，令工人黨擁有的國會議席增加到9個（包括2個[[非選區議員|非選區議席]]）。[[新加坡人民黨|新加坡人民黨]]在國會裏也有一個非選區議席<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sg.news.yahoo.com/wp-s-lee-li-lian-wins-punggol-east-by-election-150627675.html|title=WP's Lee Li Lian takes Punggol East by decisive margin|date=2013-01-26|work=Yahoo! Newsroom|accessdate=2015-08-23|location=Singapore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018233357/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/wp-s-lee-li-lian-wins-punggol-east-by-election-150627675.html|archive-date=2015-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

本次大選是新加坡建國總理[[李光耀|李光耀]]去世後當地舉行的首場大選，而1965年新加坡獨立後出生的選民人數也已經突破選民總數的五成，為歷史上首見<ref name="mp">{{cite news|title=新加坡9·11大選 反對派聲音浮現|date=2015-08-26|work=明報|location=香港}}</ref>。自2011年大選以來，行動黨政府已經借助設立[[我們的新加坡對話會|我們的新加坡對話會]]、派官員出席電視論壇等方式，希望營造行動黨會聽取民眾意見的形象<ref>{{cite web|url=http://asiapacific.anu.edu.au/newmandala/2013/02/01/managing-voice-exit-and-loyalty-in-singapore/|title=Managing voice, exit and loyalty in Singapore|last=Chua|first=Daniel|date=2013-02-01|work=New Mandela|publisher=Coral Bell School of Asia Pacific Affairs, Australian National University|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919215130/http://asiapacific.anu.edu.au/newmandala/2013/02/01/managing-voice-exit-and-loyalty-in-singapore/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並希望借助新加坡獨立50週年（SG50）慶祝活動，令國民感到更自豪，令行動黨的民望變得更高<ref name="st">{{cite news|title=選情料激烈 或邁向多黨制|date=2015-08-26|work=星島日報|pages=A26}}</ref>，也希望民眾對李光耀的支持可以對行動黨的選情有所幫助<ref name="tg">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/10/singapore-elections-lee-hsien-loong-faces-toughest-test-yet|title=Singapore elections: Lee Hsien Loong faces toughest test yet|last=Holmes|first=Oliver|date=2015-09-10|work=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian News and Media Limited|accessdate=2015-09-10|location=Singapore|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003182454/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/10/singapore-elections-lee-hsien-loong-faces-toughest-test-yet|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，他們在2013年發表的[[新加坡人口白皮书|人口白皮書]]提議令新加坡人口在2030年上升到690萬人，卻引起民眾不滿，更引起在當地罕有發生的示威<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/02/20132169114441474.html|title=Singapore seethes over population plan|last=Tan|first=Heather|date=2013-02-17|work=Al Jaazera English|publisher=Al Jaazera Media Network|accessdate=2015-09-10|location=Singapore|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005092413/http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/02/20132169114441474.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，和上一屆大選相同的是，收入不均、房屋價格和交通問題仍然是本屆大選的選舉議題，當中[[新加坡地鐵|地鐵]]列車延誤和停駛更可以拖累政府的民望<ref name="tg"/><ref>{{cite news|author=李慧敏|url=http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%BE%8C%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%89%E8%80%80%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%20%E8%AE%8A%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A%E6%8B%89%E9%8B%B8/web_tc/article/20150907/s00014/1441562001111|title=後李光耀時代大選 變與不變拉鋸|date=2015-09-07|work=明報|accessdate=2015-09-10|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193110/http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%BE%8C%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%89%E8%80%80%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%20%E8%AE%8A%E8%88%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A%E6%8B%89%E9%8B%B8/web_tc/article/20150907/s00014/1441562001111|dead-url=no}}</ref>。按照當地規定，當地年滿21歲的公民都擁有投票權<ref name="mp"/>；當地新一代對行動黨執政初期新加坡創造的經濟奇蹟產生的共鳴遠遜於他們的祖輩，而且比起[[一黨獨大|一黨獨大]]，他們更偏好多元政治和不同的政見<ref name="st"/>。選民也希望有作用的反對派可以制衡行動黨和提升新加坡國際形象<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rsis.edu.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/CO15173.pdf|title=Singapore’s GE 2015: Not Quite a Watershed Election|last=Singh|first=Bilveer|date=2015-08-18|publisher=S. Rajaratnam School of International Studies|accessdate=2015-09-10|location=Singapore|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191253/https://www.rsis.edu.sg/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/CO15173.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

