===行动党拿工人党市镇会开刀===
执政的行动党在竞选期间，不断拿国会最大反对党工人党辖下的阿裕尼-后港-榜鹅东市镇会的财务疏漏予以抨击。<ref name="huaini">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/09/150912_viewpoint_singapore_election|title=觀點：從新加坡大選看民權與公民社會|date=2015-09-12|author=胡愛妮|publisher=BBC中文网|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826071147/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/09/150912_viewpoint_singapore_election|dead-url=no}}</ref>市镇会是由各区议员组成的法定团体，负责打理区内的管理事宜。工人党党魁[[刘程强|刘程强]]于9月2日在后港的首场群众大会，全程以[[潮州话|潮州话]]发表演讲，说如犯法，早被捉。他指行动党过去四年对工人党“诸多为难”，不停地以市镇会议题“抹黑工人党”。总理李显龙也在同晚的另一场群众大会上以英语表示，某些反对党做错事后，要选民往前看，因为往后看就会看见“黑尾巴”。总理也指“如果新加坡的政治水平只是从政者不坐牢便可，我们就有严重的问题了”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.enanyang.my/news/20150903/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E9%A6%96%E5%9C%BA%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A-%E6%9C%9D%E9%87%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%BD%AE%E7%9A%86%E6%8C%A4%E7%88%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%BA/|title=新加坡大选首场群众大会 朝野人潮皆挤爆会场|publisher=南洋商报|date=2015-09-03|access-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826152905/http://www.enanyang.my/news/20150903/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E9%A6%96%E5%9C%BA%E7%BE%A4%E4%BC%97%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A-%E6%9C%9D%E9%87%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%BD%AE%E7%9A%86%E6%8C%A4%E7%88%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%BA/|archive-date=2017-08-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.facebook.com/shinmindailynewsxinmingribao/photos/a.358346434223942.79082.357787027613216/925909970800916/?type=3&theater|publisher=新明日报|title=潮州怒汉炮轰行动党 如犯法早被捉|date=2015-09-03|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213104750/https://www.facebook.com/shinmindailynewsxinmingribao/photos/a.358346434223942.79082.357787027613216/925909970800916/?type=3&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===对民主党党魁展开攻击===
行动党也对新加坡民主党党魁[[徐顺全|徐顺全]]发动攻击。教育部兼通讯及新闻部政务部长沈颖大力抨击对手很会“出pattern”（意指耍花招）。她指徐顺全不允许他人“回味他的往事”，只要提起往事，他会认为是在攻击其人格；她也指徐顺全另一个“pattern”（花招/花样）是先自己骂自己，然后说是他人在骂他。队友[[维文_(新加坡)|维文]]也指行动党并无“向导师捅一刀”的传统，以多年前政坛老将[[詹時中|詹時中]]离开民主党事件，暗指徐顺全忘恩负义，背叛恩师。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://zpolitics.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/constituencies-battle/story20150908-523933|title=沈颖批徐顺全很会耍花招|date=2015-09-08|publisher=联合早报|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826120235/http://zpolitics.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/constituencies-battle/story20150908-523933|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="huaini"/>然而，当时处理此案的高庭法官Warren Khoo指民主党并无恶意中伤詹时中，可以说是詹时中咎由自取。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://yoursdp.org/publ/the_truth_about/chiam_39_s_exit_from_the_sdp/part_2_chiam_39_s_expulsion_what_really_happened/11-1-0-17|title=Part 2: Chiam's expulsion - What really happened?|publisher=Singapore Democratic Party|date=2010-04-06|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116084347/http://yoursdp.org/publ/the_truth_about/chiam_39_s_exit_from_the_sdp/part_2_chiam_39_s_expulsion_what_really_happened/11-1-0-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===副总理尚达曼表现亮眼===
行动党籍副总理兼财政部长尚达曼表现亮眼，于9月5日晚上在武吉班让单选区的群众大会上发表近半小时的演讲。他以各经济理由解释为何不可实施反对党政策；同时他也认可政府之前对于任人唯贤的思维方向是错误的。尚达曼的表现使得朝野双方都大为认可。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mothership.sg/2015/09/dpm-tharmans-rally-speech-is-the-only-reason-why-people-still-have-hope-in-pap/|title=DPM Tharman’s rally speech is the only reason why people still have hope in PAP|date=2015-09-06|author=Jeanette Tan|publisher=Mothership.sg|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826102546/https://mothership.sg/2015/09/dpm-tharmans-rally-speech-is-the-only-reason-why-people-still-have-hope-in-pap/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

