===各方反应===
总理李显龙于结果完全公布后的数小时后，在9月12日早晨感谢国人给予强而有力的支持，及其托付的重任。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/ge2015-strong-mandate-means-mps-must-work-extra-hard-to-serve-says-pm-lee|title=GE2015: Strong mandate means MPs must work extra hard to serve, says PM Lee|date=2015-09-12|publisher=The Straits Times|access-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825233732/http://www.straitstimes.com/politics/ge2015-strong-mandate-means-mps-must-work-extra-hard-to-serve-says-pm-lee|archive-date=2017-08-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

革新党党魁肯尼斯·惹耶勒南在抽样计票结果公布后向媒体发言，说此结果并非人民对执政党经济政策的委托，而是对独裁主义与洗脑之委托。得到此结果可归咎于控制国人住房、储蓄、工作，也管制所有媒体，同时并没有独立的选举局。这相当于朝鲜和中国的情况。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=JOT4ABvOlB8|title=Kenneth Jeyaretnam: S'poreans get the govt they deserve|publisher=Mediacorp Channel 5|date=2015-09-11|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912061033/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JOT4ABvOlB8&app=desktop|dead-url=no}}</ref>

工人党秘书长刘程强在落选后欲向行动党传话，表示建立人民与国家机构，如公共服务业、司法体制和主流媒体的互信是重要的。“将这些机构政治化，以捞取政治资本，对我而言是违反新加坡国家利益的。”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sg.news.yahoo.com/ge2015--blue-skies-darken-for-workers--party-211144188.html|title=GE2015: Blue skies darken for Workers' Party|author=Nicholas Yong|publisher=Yahoo Singapore News|date=2015-09-12|access-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826120913/https://sg.news.yahoo.com/ge2015--blue-skies-darken-for-workers--party-211144188.html|archive-date=2017-08-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===结果分析===
即使本次大选面对反对派角逐所有选区，惟选举结果却让许多新加坡人感到惊讶。执政的行动党获得全国高达69.9%的选票，不但没有丢失任何议席，反而从反对党工人党手中以微差重夺榜鹅东单选区，工人党则以微差保住阿裕尼集选区。在所有选区中，由副总理[[尚达曼|尚达曼]]领军的裕廊集选区团队获得79.3%的成绩，是行动党得票率最高的选区。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mothership.sg/2015/09/third-time-lucky-for-prime-minister-lee-hsien-loong-as-pap-scored-69-9-and-won-8389-seats/|title=Third time lucky for Prime Minister Lee Hsien Loong, as PAP scored 69.9% and won 83/89 seats|author=Martino Tan|publisher=Mothership.sg|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2017-08-25|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826011222/https://mothership.sg/2015/09/third-time-lucky-for-prime-minister-lee-hsien-loong-as-pap-scored-69-9-and-won-8389-seats/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

当地公民媒体网络公民（The Online Citizen）的主编许渊臣也对结果感到震惊。他表示多数选民未必将候选人的素质考虑在内。在本次大选开战前，执政党不断强调如投反对党，执政党无法继续执政，这或许导致选民担心影响该国政局。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/09/150911_singapore_election_result_hm|title=新加坡大选：执政党“出乎意料”高票蝉联执政|date=2015-09-11|author=李慧敏|publisher=BBC中文网|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826092056/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world/2015/09/150911_singapore_election_result_hm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

也有评论指即使行动党高票胜出，也并没有得到人民的委托。这是因为行动党选票的剧增主要来自低收入的弱势群体。他们可能会到邻里的咖啡店攻击行动党政府的政策，参加反对党的群众大会，不过由于他们可能害怕失去政府给予的各种津贴、福利等等，故而暗地里把票投给执政党。而且，行动党随后举行胜选演讲，出席人数少之又少；一群着白衣的行动党人站在勿洛巴刹（菜市场）外，无人上前恭贺，候选人[[林瑞生|林瑞生]]得到商店里向几名外籍店员握手。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theonlinecitizen.com/2015/09/14/how-pap-did-not-have-the-peoples-mandate-despite-landslide-victory/|title=How PAP did not have the people’s mandate despite landslide victory|date=2015-09-14|publisher=The Online Citizen|author=Savvy Artist|accessdate=2017-08-26|archive-date=2017-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720075913/https://www.theonlinecitizen.com/2015/09/14/how-pap-did-not-have-the-peoples-mandate-despite-landslide-victory/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

